Reviewed-by: Bjorn Andersson <bjorn.andersson@linaro.org>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20200418134703.1760-1-tangbin@cmss.chinamobile.com
Signed-off-by: Joerg Roedel <jroedel@suse.de>
